statements: SELECT * FROM QuantumDataPackets;
SELECT packet_id, source_node, destination_node FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE packet_size > 100;
SELECT * FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE routing_algorithm = 'Dijkstra';
SELECT packet_id, source_node, destination_node, packet_size FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE destination_node = 'NodeB';
SELECT packet_id, source_node, destination_node FROM QuantumDataPackets ORDER BY packet_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE packet_size > 100 ORDER BY packet_id DESC;
SELECT packet_id, source_node, destination_node FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE routing_algorithm='A*';
SELECT destination_node, packet_size FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE source_node='NodeA' AND routing_algorithm='Dijkstra' ORDER BY packet_size ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_packets FROM QuantumDataPackets WHERE source_node='NodeB';
SELECT AVG(packet_size) AS average_size, MAX(packet_size) AS max_size FROM QuantumDataPackets;
SELECT * FROM quantum_packets;
SELECT packet_id, source_id, destination_id FROM quantum_packets WHERE packet_id = 1;
SELECT quantum_data FROM quantum_packets WHERE source_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM routing_optimizations ORDER BY optimization_id DESC;
SELECT packet_id, COUNT(packet_id) FROM routing_optimizations GROUP BY packet_id;
SELECT * FROM routing_optimizations WHERE optimization_id = 1;
SELECT packet_id, optimization_result FROM routing_optimizations WHERE optimization_result = 'Successful';
SELECT packet_id, optimization_result FROM routing_optimizations WHERE packet_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT avg(optimization_id), count(packet_id) FROM routing_optimizations GROUP BY optimization_result;
SELECT packet_id, optimization_result FROM routing_optimizations ORDER BY optimization_result DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumNodes;
SELECT node_id, node_name FROM QuantumNodes WHERE node_id = 1;
SELECT node_name, location FROM QuantumNodes ORDER BY node_name DESC;
SELECT connection_type FROM QuantumConnections WHERE node1_id = 2 AND node2_id = 3;
SELECT packet_id, packet_size, received FROM QuantumPackets WHERE received = FALSE;
SELECT * FROM QuantumNodes;
SELECT * FROM QuantumConnections WHERE connection_type = 'fiber';
SELECT node_name, location FROM QuantumNodes WHERE node_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT packet_id, packet_size, source_node_id, destination_node_id FROM QuantumPackets WHERE received = FALSE ORDER BY packet_size DESC;
SELECT node_id, node_name, location FROM QuantumNodes ORDER BY node_name ASC, location DESC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_packets ORDER BY packet_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT packet_id, source_address, destination_address FROM quantum_packets WHERE packet_size > 100 ORDER BY packet_size ASC, creation_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT node_name, node_location, node_status FROM quantum_routing_nodes WHERE node_status = 'active';
SELECT link_id, source_node_id, destination_node_id, link_speed FROM quantum_links WHERE link_speed >= 100 ORDER BY link_speed DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_routing_logs ORDER BY log_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_packets WHERE packet_size > 100 ORDER BY creation_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT packet_id, source_address, destination_address FROM quantum_packets WHERE creation_timestamp < NOW() AND creation_timestamp > NOW() - INTERVAL '1 hour' ORDER BY creation_timestamp;
SELECT node_id, node_name, node_location, node_status FROM quantum_routing_nodes WHERE node_status = 'ACTIVE';
SELECT * FROM quantum_links WHERE link_speed > 1000 ORDER BY link_capacity DESC LIMIT 3;

SELECT p.packet_id, p.source_address, p.destination_address, r.node_name AS source_node, r2.node_name AS destination_node FROM quantum_packets p JOIN quantum_routing_logs l ON p.packet_id = l.packet_id JOIN quantum_routing_nodes r ON l.source_node_id = r.node_id JOIN quantum_routing_nodes r2 ON l.destination_node_id = r2.node_id;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT device_id, device_name, quantum_capability FROM quantum_devices WHERE device_type='Quantum Computer';
SELECT packet_id, packet_size, arrival_time FROM quantum_packets ORDER BY arrival_time DESC;
SELECT route_id, source_device, destination_device, hop_count FROM quantum_routing WHERE hop_count > 3;
SELECT link_id, transmitted_packets, successful_packets, transmission_rate FROM quantum_performance WHERE transmission_rate > 100.00;
SELECT device_id, device_name, device_type FROM quantum_devices WHERE device_type = 'qubit';
SELECT packet_id, source_device, destination_device, arrival_time FROM quantum_packets ORDER BY arrival_time DESC;
SELECT link_id, source_device, destination_device, link_capacity FROM quantum_links WHERE link_capacity > 100 ORDER BY link_capacity ASC;
SELECT route_path, hop_count FROM quantum_routing WHERE source_device = 3 AND destination_device = 6;
SELECT performance_id, transmitted_packets, successful_packets, transmission_rate FROM quantum_performance WHERE transmission_rate > 4.5 ORDER BY successful_packets DESC;
